The P-11 is the pistol that propelled Kel-Tec to respectability and even stardom in our Industry. The P-11 is, of course, double action only. It has a hammer, but the hammer never stands. Herein lies its safety feature: in addition to the firing pin block safety that prevents firing if the pistol is dropped, the only way the pistol will fire is by a stiff deliberate pull of the trigger, long travel double action pull with pressure of 8 to 10 pounds. The Kel-Tec is good pistol. Out of several hundred we have sold over the past three decades, we have sent fewer than 20 back to the factory for repair or service. This small pistol, however, may not be suitable for people unfamiliar with automatics. title: For Sale:  Burris 4X EER Pistol Scope - Target Turrents - Adjustable Objective AO
postcontent:
Up for sale is a used Burris Extended Eye Relief 4 Power Telescopic sight for pistols.  It is silver.  The optics are in good condition but the previous owner scratched the outside in the mounting area.  It has a duplex reticle

A nice feature of this scope is that the objective lens is adjustable to change the focus, with markings from 25 and 200 yards.  You can focus a little close than 25 yards, that is just where the first mark is.

Another nice feature is the target turrets.  You can use your fingers to remove the turret covers and adjust for windage and elevation.  The turrets are clearly marked in white on black.   There are tall hash marks at whole numbers and short hash mark at the halves.    One click is a half mark, which works out to 1/2 inch at 100 yards.  There is a label to remind you inside the turret cover.  The scale runs from from 0 to 28 in even numbers. The barrel of the turret is marked like a micrometer so that you can count how many turns you make.  The count goes from 0 to 3 turns in whole numbers.

I will be in town for the NRA meeting. I can deliver it then or meet you in Louisville, Lexington, Cincinnati or points in between.

I bought this scope for my Contender but have better luck with the rifle barrels than with the pistol. I am also selling a 10 inch .22 LR Contender pistol barrel and some .357 Max ammo.

I am asking $225 or best offer.
